h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User, Exchange House User

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of *Task* input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow: 
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Disbursement sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Create" link from left menu under task .
* Show Landing Page of "Task".

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show Task" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get [List of all "Task" from server|guide:ListRmsTaskActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show *Task* information in grid view.
** Blank input form on top to create new *Task*.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].